name: GoogleUserDuplicates_DuplicateUsersByID
query:
SELECT id, customSchemas_Tools4ever_ID, customSchemas_Tools4ever_Type, givenName, familyName, primaryEmail
FROM f_App_GoogleUserDuplicates_ListUsers
WHERE customSchemas_Tools4ever_ID IN (
  SELECT customSchemas_Tools4ever_ID
  FROM f_App_GoogleUserDuplicates_ListUsers
  WHERE length(customSchemas_Tools4ever_ID) > 0
  GROUP BY customSchemas_Tools4ever_ID
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
  )
ORDER BY customSchemas_Tools4ever_ID
